<br>
Ask the Iskar Necro in the Top of the Library &quot;what rare books&quot; and he will tell you about how he wants the Tome of Dark Power in the library but they cant find it.<br>
<br>
I dont remember the exact location, but it is on a shelf like the other book you look for in the library.<br>
<br>
Take the book back to him and he will tell you it is locked and for you to take it to Elder Tal Alman (sp) He is the elder you first see when you zone to PoT.<br>
<br>
Give him the book and he will give it back to you as an unlocked or open Tome of Dark Power. <br>
<br>
Take this back to the Iksar Necro and he will tell you that pages are missing and give you back a book with 8 slots and wants you to fill the book with the missing pages.<br>
<br>
I found the Page #13 in PoN off the treants (regular treant)<br>
PoI<br>
3,5,7,11,17,19<br>
<br>
PoN<br>
2,3,5,7,13,17,19<br>
<br>
Between PoI and Pon that is all 8 pages. I imagine all pages can drop in either plane though.<br>
<br>
The reward is : Cloak of the Wise AC7 7STA 7CHA 7WIS 7INT 45hp 45mana. 0.8 wgt. all/all. Tradeable.<br>
<br>
Some people are knocking it, but I don't think it's too bad. You can get those pages while gettin exp and parchments for spells.<br>
